{"tid":1853772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"微信：對散佈疫情謠言的賬號進行限期或永久封禁處理","createTime":"2020-01-31T07:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T07:17:32.000Z","uid":252871,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"95cc9cc32ec9f8092590a32b07e39202cd325555","tid":1853772,"uid":252871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:05:09.000Z","msg":"1月25日，微信安全中心發布《關於新型冠狀病毒肺炎相關謠言專項治理的公告》。 《公告》表示：新型冠狀病毒肺炎正在全國各地持續傳播，引發社會廣泛關注。與此同時，各類&ldquo;網傳&rdquo;、&ldquo;聽說&rdquo;類謠言信息也不斷刺激著大家的恐慌情緒。 《刑法修正案（九）》明確規定：&ldquo;編造虛假的險情、疫情、災情、警情，在信息網絡或者其他媒體上傳播，或者明知是上述虛假信息，故意在信息網絡或者其他媒體上傳播，嚴重擾亂社會秩序的，處3年以下有期徒刑、拘役或者管制；造成嚴重後果的，處3年以上7年以下有期徒刑。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.sina.com.cn/chanjing/gsnews/2020-01-26/doc-iihnzhha4727852.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.com.cn%2Fchanjing%2Fgsnews%2F2020-01-26%2Fdoc-iihnzhha4727852.shtml&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6DwikyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=b1e43ac1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://finance.sina.com.cn/chanjing/gsnews/2020-01-26/doc-iihnzhha4727852.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08396c6c227d59d51689014adbcd3949fa8ae3b1","tid":1853772,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:05:31.000Z","msg":"殺人啦"},{"pid":"30be7f75ccfb1938edaa017d9be1ceff767dc8f0","tid":1853772,"uid":37325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:05:50.000Z","msg":"被病死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f758769c79463c9a60c0f52945a2d1085bdfe66","tid":1853772,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T07:05:58.000Z","msg":"搞唔掂了, 要完全封鎖消息"},{"pid":"426ccb13480e1211636dd89077da408ae05d13a7","tid":1853772,"uid":329842,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202